Suggestion.create(:id => 23, :name => "Interactive Cologne", :occurrence => "17.06.2013 - 23.06.2013", :description => "INTERACTIVE COLOGNE is a one-week festival coming up in June 2013.\r\nOur aim is to bring Cologne’s hacker, startup and creative communities together,\r\npromote them on both a national and international level,\r\nas well as letting the world know how awesome Cologne is!\r\n\r\nThe following program items are offered:\r\n\r\nInteractive Hackathon:\r\n\r\nTalented web & app developers, hackers and designers gather at INTERACTIVE COLOGNE to kick-off their own or others’ projects, refine or complete code collaboratively or just experiment - preferably open source.\r\n\r\nWe're offering hacks like:\r\n\r\n- Mobile Hack Track\r\n- Nodecopter Hack Track\r\n- Rails Girls Cologne\r\n- Music Hack Days\r\n- 3D Printing Hack\r\n- City Serious Games SpotOn Hack\r\n- Open Data Hack\r\n- Small Hardware Hack Tracks (Anykey)\r\n- Techtalks & Lightningtalks\r\n\r\nInteractive Startup Conference:\r\n\r\nStartups, techies, investors and entrepreneurs will meet in a creative atmosphere to discuss hot topics and network with other technology industry professionals who share similar passions, and social interests. Therefore we offer different formats:\r\n\r\nWe're offering talks like:\r\n\r\n- Startup Breakfast\r\n- Lightning Talks\r\n- Biz Talks & Panel Discussions\r\n- Business-Model Talks\r\n- Finance Talks\r\n- Technical-Talets Talks\r\n- Dating startup and startup pitches\r\n\r\nInteractive Business Meetups:\r\n\r\n- HGNF Finanzierungstag\r\n- Web de Cologne\r\n\r\nInteractive Creativity:\r\n\r\n- c/o pop\r\n- C'n'B\r\n\r\nPricing:\r\n\r\n- Webmontag & Warmup Party: free\r\n- Hack'n'Tech, Startup & Startup Breakfast: 25 EUR per participant ticket / 50 EUR visitor ticket\r\n- Kölsch.rb: free\r\n- Parties & Afterparties: free\r\n- Web De Cologne: 50 EUR (for WdC members free)\r\n- DevHouseFriday Chillout: free\r\n- c/o pop festival 70 EUR\r\n- C'n'B Convention 80 EUR\r\n\r\nMore information: http://interactive-cologne.com", :place => "Cologne\r\n\r\nHGNC Finanzierungstag:\r\nUniversity of Cologne, \"Neues Seminargebäude\" (building 106)\r\n\r\nWebmontag & Warmup-Party:\r\nWohngemeinschaft, Richard-Wagner-Str. 39, 50674 Köln\r\n\r\nHackathon & Startup Conference: Trinitatiskirche, Filzengraben 6  50676 Cologne, Germany\r\n\r\nAfterparty:\r\nWohngemeinschaft, Richard-Wagner-Str. 39, 50674 Köln\r\n\r\nc/o Pop: \r\ndiverse Locations im Belgischen Viertel & Umgebung\r\n\r\nC'n'B:\r\nKölnischer Kunstverein (Hahnenstraße 6, 50667 Cologne, Germany) & Fritz Thyssen Stiftung (Apostelnkloster 13-15, 50672 Köln) ", :more => {"http://twitter.com/interactive_cgn\r"=>"https://www.facebook.com/InteractiveCologne"})
